  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/8c81a3a50da621f48db627b1a267533e.avif?t=1761052622\" width=640 height=100 /></span><strong>POLYGON</strong> is a tactical multiplayer team 1st person shooter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using various weapons, you will battle with <strong>up to 32 players</strong> on large-scale maps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Properly managing your arsenal and skills, you will lead your team to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with up to 16 players to fight in furious PvP matches. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Group up with your friends in the squad to bring the teamplay to another level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large arsenal is available – each weapon has a real prototype! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between assault rifles, PDWs, LMGs, DMRs and Sniper rifles to find your play style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A customization system will help you to adjust your weapon to your needs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change sights, handles, muzzle devices and accessories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, you can unlock many skins to show off on a battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into battle in any location: from spacious valley to narrow subway. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different maps – different situations!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is constantly being improved. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the outcome of the battle using new weapons and skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends and explore new locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOPMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive controls and obvious gameplay make the game simple and fun. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >POLYGON can be run on outdated PCs and show all its all capabilities on modern computers – thanks to the <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launched by cutting-edge innovations, the Unreal engine gives the POLYGON game amazing graphics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the moment, the game is being developed by <strong>only one person</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, my name is <strong>Nick</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet me and our friendly Moderators on Discord where we can help you and tell you more about the game :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We also often hold various events where you can get in-game rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into battle with POLYGON!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/8c81a3a50da621f48db627b1a267533e.avif?t=1761052622\" width=640 height=100 /></span><strong>POLYGON</strong> is a tactical multiplayer team 1st person shooter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using various weapons, you will battle with <strong>up to 32 players</strong> on large-scale maps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Properly managing your arsenal and skills, you will lead your team to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with up to 16 players to fight in furious PvP matches. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Group up with your friends in the squad to bring the teamplay to another level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large arsenal is available – each weapon has a real prototype! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between assault rifles, PDWs, LMGs, DMRs and Sniper rifles to find your play style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A customization system will help you to adjust your weapon to your needs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change sights, handles, muzzle devices and accessories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, you can unlock many skins to show off on a battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into battle in any location: from spacious valley to narrow subway. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different maps – different situations!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is constantly being improved. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the outcome of the battle using new weapons and skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends and explore new locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOPMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive controls and obvious gameplay make the game simple and fun. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >POLYGON can be run on outdated PCs and show all its all capabilities on modern computers – thanks to the <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launched by cutting-edge innovations, the Unreal engine gives the POLYGON game amazing graphics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the moment, the game is being developed by <strong>only one person</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, my name is <strong>Nick</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet me and our friendly Moderators on Discord where we can help you and tell you more about the game :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We also often hold various events where you can get in-game rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into battle with POLYGON!</strong></p>",
